    SlabOnDeck: Property for 2D analytical elements representing a slab on a corrugated deck. Generally used to represent concrete on metal deck.

      • getDeckSpacing

        public Double getDeckSpacing()
        Centre-centre distance between the ribs. Measured perpendicular to the rib direction. If this length is greater than the sum of BottomWidth and TopWidth, the deck is trapezoidal. If lesser, the deck has a dovetail shape. Property has a quantity of type Length measured in [m]. (Required)
